Class BooleanSubscription

    Subscription

    public final class BooleanSubscription
extends java.lang.Object
implements Subscription
    Subscription that can be checked for status such as in a loop inside an Observable to exit the loop if unsubscribed.
    See Also:
    Rx.Net equivalent BooleanDisposable

      • unsubscribe

        public final void unsubscribe()
        Description copied from interface: Subscription
        Stop receiving notifications on the Subscriber that was registered when this Subscription was received.

        This allows unregistering an Subscriber before it has finished receiving all events (ie. before onCompleted is called).

        Specified by:
